CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 25, 1966, pg, 1B, reads: "Mrs. Clemente - Like all dutiful wives, Vera Clemente enjoys preparing for her husband his favorite meals. Naturally he prefers Puerto Rican food.  Mrs. Clemente is expected  to give birth to her second child next month.  She returned to Puerto Rico for the event. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of pregnant Vera Clemente, wife of Roberto Clemente, standing at kitchen sink, in their apartment in East Liberty
